l weapon art:<br/><br/>To get full power (Damage) you gotta hold down the weapon art and once you&apos;ve sheathed your katana it will be powered up in three stages where it flashes a blue light near the sheathe at every stage. <br/>The first glow will have 33 % of the damage and at second flash 66 % and lastly at third glow it will have 100 % of the damage (same damage as now). This would allows players to use this weapon with skill and not spam the weapon art as much.<br/><br/>The percentage I&apos;ve given is just an example and not what it has to be. I just want this weapon to be fair and good at the same time because it&apos;s a really cool design and I don&apos;t want it&apos;s potential to be gone forever. <br/><br/><br/></p><textarea style="display: none;" class="txt-comment-ed"></textarea><div class="clearfix"><a role="button" data-toggle="collapse" href="#zz-16783440" class="cmt-reply pull-right" href=""><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-share-alt"></span>Reply</a><a id="btnExpandComment" role="button" data-toggle="collapse" href="#replies-16783440" class="cmt-reply pull-right" href=""><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-share-alt"></span>Replies (<span class="replies">0</span>)</a><div class="vote pull-right"><section class="t-up"><span></span><p>0</p><i class="add">+1</i></section><section class="t-down"><span></span><p>0</p><i class="sub">-1</i></section></div></div><div class="collapse-com transparent"><div class="col-trigger collapse" id="zz-16783440"><div class="ng-scope"><textarea id="dcomment" class="ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-invalid ng-invalid-required" placeholder="Input your comments:"></textarea><button id="btn-16783440" class="btn btn-default btnPostReply"><i class="glyphicon glyphicon-pencil"></i> Submit</button><img id="newCommentAvatar" src="/images/avatar.png"/></div></div></div></div><div class="clearfix"></div><ul class="children collapse" id="replies-16783440"></ul></li></ul></li>
			
